<TABLE>
<A NAME=POEM1></A>
<TR ALIGN=LEFT VALIGN=TOP><TD><P><FONT SIZE=+1>toddler&#8217;s first
<br>
one small step
<br>
toward the moon in the window
</FONT></TD></TR> <TR ALIGN=RIGHT VALIGN=TOP><TD>
Mathew V. Spano
<P>&nbsp;</TD></TR>
<A NAME=POEM3></A>
<TR ALIGN=LEFT VALIGN=TOP><TD><P><FONT SIZE=+1>autumn moonlight
<br>
a migrant worker sings
<br>
his way home
</FONT></TD></TR> <TR ALIGN=RIGHT VALIGN=TOP><TD>
Melissa Spurr
<P>&nbsp;</TD></TR>
<A NAME=POEM5></A>
<TR ALIGN=LEFT VALIGN=TOP><TD><P><FONT SIZE=+1>smoke drifts
<br>
from a fajita stand
<br>
plaza autumn
</FONT></TD></TR> <TR ALIGN=RIGHT VALIGN=TOP><TD>
Ann K. Schwader
<P>&nbsp;</TD></TR>
<A NAME=POEM7></A>
<TR ALIGN=LEFT VALIGN=TOP><TD><P><FONT SIZE=+1>the right shoes
<br>
in the wrong size
<br>
October moon
</FONT></TD></TR> <TR ALIGN=RIGHT VALIGN=TOP><TD>
Glenn G. Coats
<P>&nbsp;</TD></TR>
<A NAME=POEM9></A>
<TR ALIGN=LEFT VALIGN=TOP><TD><P><FONT SIZE=+1>scent of balsam&nbsp;&#8212;
<br>
shapes of geese
<br>
held in the mist
</FONT></TD></TR> <TR ALIGN=RIGHT VALIGN=TOP><TD>
Diana Webb
<P>&nbsp;</TD></TR>
</TABLE></TD>
